<div class="content-header">Linux Install</div>

<div class="content">
    The <code>.tar.gz</code> Linux installation is available <a href="/resources/scripts/linux_install.tar.gz">here</a>.
</div>

<div class="content">
    The download includes an <code>install.sh</code> installation script.
    Change to the directory containing <code>install.sh</code>, and run <code>./install.sh</code> as root to install.
</div>

<div class="content">
    Uninstall by running the included <code>uninstall.sh</code> script.
</div>

<div class="content-section">Java</div>

<div class="content">
    Java installation is required.
    The application has been tested with version Java 12.0.2.
    Set <code>JAVA_HOME</code> to the Java installation directory, and add <code>$JAVA_HOME/bin</code> to <code>PATH</code>.
</div>

<div class="content-section">Startup</div>

<div class="content">
    The tasks application starts with the command <code>musicxmltasks</code>.
</div>

<div class="content">
    If <code>gtk-launch</code> is available on your Linux system, a launch icon appears.
</div>
